  "stem": "<p>Which expression represents the product of (a<sup>&minus;4</sup>b<sup>2</sup>c<sup>3</sup>) and (a<sup>6</sup>c<sup>3</sup> + b<sup>5</sup>c<sup>&minus;8</sup>)?</p>",
